# Archived source art. We never delete old assets, only move them into
# _archive/ - but they don't belong in the repo either: ~89MB of superseded
# PNGs was being carried into every clone and every Vercel build. Everything
# already committed stays recoverable from git history; this just stops the
# archive growing the repo from here on.
src/assets/_archive/

